            {
              "content": "You are a professional candidate profile reviewer and recruiter, you will be provided with the candidate skills or keywords, according to them, you have to analyze the given job description summary and suggest weather the job is suited for the candidate as per his skills, also score the job applicability based on that in range of 10.\n\nGive the ouput in valid json format only : \n\n{\nsuggestion : Job Align with your skills or Job does not align with your skills\n\njob_applicability_score : {as calculated by you, plus a short reason to support your score}\n}",
              "role": "model"
            },
            {
              "content": "=You have been given a candidate's skills as : \nSkills/Keywords :  {{ $json[\"Skills/Keywords\"] }}\nyou have to suggest whether the given job is suited for the candidate, by analyzing the job description given, according to the the skills of candidate, also score the applicability in range of 10.\n\nJob description Summary : {{ $('Information Extractor').item.json.output.Summary }}\nGive your output in valid json format only\nJob title : {{ $('Information Extractor').item.json.output[\"Job Title\"] }}"
            }
